---
layout: base.njk
title: Portfolio
description: "Real Oregon & SW Washington weddings coordinated by Amore Coordination — Skamania Lodge, Hoyt Arboretum, Oregon Golf Club, and more. Browse full galleries."
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <p class="section__eyebrow">Selected Celebrations</p>
  <h1 class="page-hero__title">Portfolio</h1>
  <p class="page-hero__sub">A few of the couples and venues it's been my joy to work with across Oregon and Washington.</p>
</section>

<section class="portfolio portfolio--page">
  <div class="grid">
    {% for p in portfolio %}
      {% set hasGallery = p.slug and galleries[p.slug] %}
      <a class="card{% if hasGallery %} card--gallery{% endif %}" href="{% if hasGallery %}/portfolio/{{ p.slug }}/{% else %}/contact/{% endif %}">
        <img src="{{ p.cover }}" alt="{{ p.couple }} wedding at {{ p.venue }}, {{ p.location }} — coordinated by Amore Coordination" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="card__veil">
          <p class="card__couple">{{ p.couple }}</p>
          <p class="card__venue">{{ p.venue }} · {{ p.location }}</p>
          <p class="card__photog">{{ p.photog }}</p>
          {% if hasGallery %}<span class="card__view">View Gallery · {{ galleries[p.slug].length }} Photos</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="cta-band__inner">
    <p class="section__eyebrow">Your Wedding, Next</p>
    <h2 class="section__title">I'd love to hear your story.</h2>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--dark">Start Your Inquiry</a>
  </div>
</section>
